<h3 id="lru-缓存机制" tabindex="-1"><a class="header-anchor" href="#lru-缓存机制" aria-hidden="true">#</a> <a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/lru-cache/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LRU 缓存机制<ExternalLinkIcon/></a></h3>
